title: Kaepernick throws 2 TD passes as 49ers snap four-game skid
text: Kaepernick throws 2 TD passes as 49ers snap four-game skid Monday, 19 October 2015 (5 minutes ago) The big plays that have eluded the 49ers most of this season showed up again, with Anquan Boldin and Torrey Smith leading the way against the very Baltimore Ravens team they helped lead to a Super Bowl victory against San Francisco three seasons ago.
